Picumnus aurifrons juruanus Gyldenstolpe, 1941
Picumnus aurifrons purusianus Todd, 1946
Picumnus aurifrons transfasciatus Hellmayr et Gyldenstolpe, 1937
Picumnus aurifrons wallacii Hargitt, 1889

